  <scopecontent id="aspace_f7854be0b26304ae0be38328a4d98c3f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Microfilm of tombstone inscriptions for the Town of Caroline, Tompkins County, New York. Also, Mr. Lockwood's correspondence and research materials concerning the genealogy of the Lockwood and related families, including cemetery records from Honeoye Falls and Lima, and notes from churches and public records in Dutchess, Livingston, Monroe, and Ulster Counties. Also, a typed report on Moses DeWitt written by Myron Melvin, 1933.</p>  </scopecontent>
